"empty, then the user will be redirected immediately if the ticket is valid, "
"without a button to click."
msgstr ""
"只有填写了内容才会显示按钮。如果留空，用户在门票验证有效后将立即被重定向。"

#: sasoEventtickets_Options.php:694
msgid "Webhooks"
msgstr "Webhooks"

#: sasoEventtickets_Options.php:695
msgid "Activate webhooks to call a service with the validation check."
msgstr "启用Webhooks，在验证检查时调用其他服务。"

#: sasoEventtickets_Options.php:695
msgid ""
"If active, each validation request from a user will trigger an URL from the "
"server side to another URL. Be carefull. This could slow down the validation "
"check. It depends how fast your service URLs are responding."
msgstr ""
"如果启用，每次用户验证请求都会从服务器端触发一个URL调用。请注意，这可能会降低"
"验证速度，取决于您的服务URL的响应速度。"

